WEBVTT

42:41.359 --> 42:42.150
Kumaran!

42:43.234 --> 42:44.484
Viji, what are you doing here?

42:44.692 --> 42:47.150
-He... his father...
-Where is your handbag?

42:47.359 --> 42:49.317
-It's there.
-God! Come soon.

42:54.609 --> 42:56.484
Are you mad? I gave
the gun for your security.

42:56.734 --> 42:58.234
And you carelessly keep it in the bag?

42:58.317 --> 42:59.442
He is a murderer.

42:59.609 --> 43:01.400
What if he gets hold of it?

43:02.067 --> 43:03.150
Irresponsible idiot!
